Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:21.37,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}全てを摑み獲れ今すぐ ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:25.11,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}真実を手に!
