Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:02.56,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}獵取一切的武士瘋狂起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:06.29,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}內燃機頻頻轟鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:08.65,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍將延續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:12.81,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使是糜爛的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:17.51,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在歎息之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:21.39,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}跟隨神風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.93,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}向著未知之處前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:28.93,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鼎沸的熱情與
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:34.13,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}薰染的靈魂勒緊胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:38.59,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}如同燃燒的火焰般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:41.11,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能在此找到自己的容身之地
